OL,7,FRoughly 70,000 members of the
OL,8,FUniversity College Union (UCU) have
OL,9,Fvoted to strike over pay, conditions
OL,10,Fand pensions, in UK-wide action.
OL,12,FThe union said that since 2009 staff
OL,13,Fpay has been cut in real terms by more
OL,14,Fthan 25 per cent, while the pensions of
OL,15,Funiversity workers have been slashed
OL,16,Fthis year by an average of 35 per cent.
